{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1230,"text":"A few years ago,"},{"time":2598,"text":"I always had this thing happening to me,"},{"time":5381,"text":"especially at family gatherings"},{"time":7165,"text":"like teas with aunts and uncles\nor something like this."},{"time":10319,"text":"When people come up to you,"},{"time":11718,"text":"and they ask you,\n\"So, what are you doing?\""},{"time":15068,"text":"And I would have\nthis magical one-word reply,"},{"time":18983,"text":"which would make everybody happy:"},{"time":21199,"text":"\"Medicine."},{"time":22549,"text":"I'm going to be a doctor.\""},{"time":23999,"text":"Very easy, that's it,\neverybody's happy and pleased."},{"time":27493,"text":"And it could be so easy,"},{"time":29111,"text":"but this effect really only lasts\nfor 30 seconds with me,"},{"time":33702,"text":"because that's then the time\nwhen one of them would ask,"},{"time":37005,"text":"\"So, in what area of medicine?"},{"time":39424,"text":"What specialty do you want to go into?\""},{"time":42326,"text":"And then I would have to strip down\nin all honesty and just say,"},{"time":46696,"text":"\"OK, so I'm fascinated with the colon."},{"time":50190,"text":"It all started with the anus,"},{"time":51691,"text":"and now it's basically\nthe whole intestinal tract.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":54638,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":56845,"text":"And this would be the moment\nwhen the enthusiasm trickled,"},{"time":60167,"text":"and it would maybe also get,\nlike, awkwardly silent in the room,"},{"time":64686,"text":"and I would think this was terribly sad,"},{"time":66935,"text":"because I do believe\nour bowels are quite charming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70356,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71980,"text":"And while we're in a time\nwhere many people are thinking about"},{"time":75073,"text":"what new superfood smoothie to make"},{"time":77372,"text":"or if gluten is maybe bad for them,"},{"time":80141,"text":"actually, hardly anyone seems to care\nabout the organ where this happens,"},{"time":85238,"text":"the concrete anatomy\nand the mechanisms behind it."},{"time":88284,"text":"And sometimes it seems to me"},{"time":89775,"text":"like we're all trying\nto figure out this magic trick,"},{"time":93036,"text":"but nobody's checking out the magician,"},{"time":95426,"text":"just because he has, like,"},{"time":96735,"text":"an embarrassing hairstyle or something."},{"time":100390,"text":"And actually,"},{"time":102841,"text":"there are reasons science\ndisliked the gut for a long time;"},{"time":106350,"text":"I have to say this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107525,"text":"So, it's complex."},{"time":108760,"text":"There's a lot of surface area --"},{"time":110318,"text":"about 40 times the area of our skin."},{"time":112546,"text":"Then, in such a tight pipe,"},{"time":114149,"text":"there are so many immune cells\nthat are being trained there."},{"time":117096,"text":"We have 100 trillion bacteria\ndoing all sorts of things --"},{"time":120307,"text":"producing little molecules."},{"time":121832,"text":"Then there's about 20 different hormones,"},{"time":124155,"text":"so we are on a very different level\nthan our genitals, for example."},{"time":127937,"text":"And the nervous system\nof our gut is so complex"},{"time":131082,"text":"that when we cut out a piece,"},{"time":132834,"text":"it's independent enough\nthat when we poke it,"},{"time":135185,"text":"it mumbles back at us, friendly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137557,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":140078,"text":"But at least those reasons are also\nthe reasons why it's so fascinating"},{"time":145092,"text":"and important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147295,"text":"It took me three steps to love the gut."},{"time":150571,"text":"So today, I invite you to follow me\non those three steps."},{"time":155096,"text":"The very first was just looking at it"},{"time":157970,"text":"and asking questions\nlike, \"How does it work?\""},{"time":161034,"text":"and \"Why does it have to look\nso weird for that sometimes?\""},{"time":165629,"text":"And it actually wasn't me asking\nthe first kind of these questions,"},{"time":169491,"text":"but my roommate."},{"time":170796,"text":"After one heavy night of partying,"},{"time":173578,"text":"he came into our shared-room kitchen,"},{"time":176747,"text":"and he said, \"Giulia, you study medicine.\nHow does pooping work?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":181846,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183911,"text":"And I did study medicine\nbut I had no idea,"},{"time":186316,"text":"so I had to go up to my room\nand look it up in different books."},{"time":189540,"text":"And I found something interesting,\nI thought, at that time."},{"time":192552,"text":"So it turns out, we don't only have\nthis outer sphincter,"},{"time":196433,"text":"we also have an inner sphincter muscle."},{"time":198365,"text":"The outer sphincter we all know,\nwe can control it,"},{"time":200782,"text":"we know what's going on there;"},{"time":202333,"text":"the inner one, we really don't."},{"time":203949,"text":"So what happens is,"},{"time":205169,"text":"when there are leftovers from digestion,"},{"time":207658,"text":"they're being delivered\nto the inner one first."},{"time":210176,"text":"This inner one will open in a reflex"},{"time":212646,"text":"and let through a little bit for testing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":216477,"text":"So, there are sensory cells"},{"time":218706,"text":"that will analyze what has been delivered:\nIs it gaseous or is it solid?"},{"time":224039,"text":"And they will then send\nthis information up to our brain,"},{"time":227158,"text":"and this is the moment\nwhen our brain knows,"},{"time":229342,"text":"\"Oh, I have to go to the toilet.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":231363,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":234452,"text":"The brain will then do\nwhat it's designed to do"},{"time":236805,"text":"with its amazing consciousness."},{"time":238593,"text":"It will mediate with our surroundings,"},{"time":241386,"text":"and it will say something like,"},{"time":242887,"text":"\"So, I checked."},{"time":244295,"text":"We are at this TEDx conference -- \""}]},{"cues":[{"time":246979,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":251083,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253378,"text":"Gaseous?"},{"time":254552,"text":"Maybe, if you're sitting on the sides,"},{"time":256812,"text":"and you know you can pull it off silently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260225,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":262089,"text":"But solid --"},{"time":263272,"text":"maybe later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264497,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":265964,"text":"Since our outer sphincter and the brain\nis connected with nervous cells,"},{"time":271418,"text":"they coordinate, cooperate,"},{"time":273460,"text":"and they put it back in a waiting line --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275805,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278054,"text":"for other times,"},{"time":279256,"text":"like, for example, when we're at home\nsitting on the couch,"},{"time":282160,"text":"we have nothing better to do,"},{"time":283743,"text":"we are free to go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285044,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":289954,"text":"Us humans are actually one\nof the very few animals that do this"},{"time":294069,"text":"in such an advanced and clean way."},{"time":296840,"text":"To be honest, I had some newfound respect"},{"time":299449,"text":"for that nice, inner sphincter dude --"},{"time":302004,"text":"not connected to nerves"},{"time":303902,"text":"that care too much about\nthe outer world or the time --"},{"time":307143,"text":"just caring about me for once."},{"time":309776,"text":"I thought that was nice."},{"time":311798,"text":"And I used to not be a great fan\nof public restrooms,"},{"time":315406,"text":"but now I can go anywhere,"},{"time":317238,"text":"because I consider it more"},{"time":318542,"text":"when that inner muscle puts a suggestion\non my daily agenda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322378,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":324121,"text":"And also I learned\nsomething else, which was:"},{"time":326872,"text":"looking closely at something\nI might have shied away from --"},{"time":331131,"text":"maybe the weirdest part of myself --"},{"time":334172,"text":"left me feeling more fearless,"},{"time":336420,"text":"and also appreciating myself more."},{"time":339166,"text":"And I think this happens a lot of times"},{"time":341207,"text":"when you look at the gut, actually."},{"time":343245,"text":"Like those funny rumbling\nnoises that happen"},{"time":346016,"text":"when you're in a group of friends"},{"time":347673,"text":"or at the office conference table,"},{"time":349423,"text":"going, like, \"Merrr, merrr...\""},{"time":352815,"text":"This is not because we're hungry."},{"time":354845,"text":"This is because our small intestine\nis actually a huge neat freak,"},{"time":358796,"text":"and it takes the time in between digestion\nto clean everything up,"},{"time":363065,"text":"resulting in those eight meters\nof gut -- really, seven of them --"},{"time":366830,"text":"being very clean\nand hardly smelling like anything."},{"time":370494,"text":"It will, to achieve this,\ncreate a strong muscular wave"},{"time":374345,"text":"that moves everything forward\nthat's been leftover after digestion."},{"time":378457,"text":"This can sometimes create a sound,"},{"time":380281,"text":"but doesn't necessarily have to always."},{"time":383372,"text":"So what we're embarrassed of\nis really a sign"},{"time":386038,"text":"of something keeping\nour insides fine and tidy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389877,"text":"Or this weird, crooked shape\nof our stomach --"},{"time":392827,"text":"a bit Quasimodo-ish."},{"time":394865,"text":"This actually makes us be able\nto put pressure on our belly"},{"time":398197,"text":"without vomiting,"},{"time":399392,"text":"like when we're laughing"},{"time":400694,"text":"and when we're doing sports,"},{"time":402067,"text":"because the pressure will go up\nand not so much sideways."},{"time":405407,"text":"This also creates this air bubble"},{"time":407316,"text":"that's usually always very visible\nin X-rays, for example,"},{"time":411535,"text":"and can sometimes, with some people,"},{"time":413352,"text":"when it gets too big,"},{"time":415217,"text":"create discomfort\nor even some sensations of pain."},{"time":418469,"text":"But for most of the people,\nis just results"},{"time":420643,"text":"that it's far easier to burp\nwhen you're laying on your left side"},{"time":423930,"text":"instead of your right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426312,"text":"And soon I moved a bit further"},{"time":428258,"text":"and started to look at the whole picture\nof our body and health."},{"time":431616,"text":"This was actually after I had heard"},{"time":434030,"text":"that someone I knew a little bit\nhad killed himself."},{"time":437489,"text":"It happened that I had been sitting\nnext to that person the day before,"},{"time":442222,"text":"and I smelled that he had very bad breath."},{"time":445869,"text":"And when I learned\nof the suicide the next day,"},{"time":448138,"text":"I thought: Could the gut have\nsomething to do with it?"},{"time":451077,"text":"And I frantically started searching\nif there were scientific papers"},{"time":454317,"text":"on the connection of gut and brain."},{"time":456904,"text":"And to my surprise, I found many."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459809,"text":"It turns out it's maybe not as simple\nas we sometimes think."},{"time":463147,"text":"We tend to think our brain\nmakes these commands"},{"time":465518,"text":"and then sends them down\nto the other organs,"},{"time":467701,"text":"and they all have to listen."},{"time":469417,"text":"But really, it's more that 10 percent\nof the nerves that connect brain and gut"},{"time":474635,"text":"deliver information\nfrom the brain to the gut."},{"time":477874,"text":"We know this, for example,\nin stressful situations,"},{"time":481029,"text":"when there are transmitters from the brain\nthat are being sensed by our gut,"},{"time":485072,"text":"so the gut will try to lower all the work,"},{"time":488666,"text":"and not be working\nand taking away blood and energy"},{"time":493208,"text":"to save energy for problem-solving."},{"time":495519,"text":"This can go as far as nervous vomiting\nor nervous diarrhea"},{"time":499040,"text":"to get rid of food that it then\ndoesn't want to digest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502869,"text":"Maybe more interestingly,"},{"time":504153,"text":"90 percent of the nervous fibers\nthat connect gut and brain"},{"time":507435,"text":"deliver information\nfrom our gut to our brain."},{"time":511296,"text":"And when you think about it a little bit,"},{"time":513274,"text":"it does make sense,\nbecause our brain is very isolated."},{"time":516902,"text":"It's in this bony skull\nsurrounded by a thick skin,"},{"time":521271,"text":"and it needs information\nto put together a feeling"},{"time":524282,"text":"of \"How am I, as a whole body, doing?\""},{"time":527893,"text":"And the gut, actually, is possibly\nthe most important advisor for the brain"},{"time":532343,"text":"because it's our largest sensory organ,"},{"time":535074,"text":"collecting information not only\non the quality of our nutrients,"},{"time":538870,"text":"but really also on how are so many\nof our immune cells doing,"},{"time":542986,"text":"or things like the hormones\nin our blood that it can sense."},{"time":545908,"text":"And it can package this information,\nand send it up to the brain."},{"time":549014,"text":"It can, there, not reach areas\nlike visual cortex or word formations --"},{"time":553783,"text":"otherwise, when we digest,"},{"time":555602,"text":"we would see funny colors\nor we would make funny noises -- no."},{"time":560123,"text":"But it can reach areas\nfor things like morality,"},{"time":563014,"text":"fear or emotional processing"},{"time":564897,"text":"or areas for self-awareness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":567377,"text":"So it does make sense"},{"time":568848,"text":"that when our body and our brain\nare putting together this feeling"},{"time":572520,"text":"of, \"How am I, as a whole body, doing?\""},{"time":574973,"text":"that the gut has something\nto contribute to this process."},{"time":580103,"text":"And it also makes sense"},{"time":581346,"text":"that people who have conditions\nlike irritable bowel syndrome"},{"time":584636,"text":"or inflammatory bowel disease"},{"time":586496,"text":"have a higher risk of having\nanxiety or depression."},{"time":589872,"text":"I think this is good information to share,"},{"time":592402,"text":"because many people will think,"},{"time":593940,"text":"\"I have this gut thing, and maybe\nI also have this mental health thing.\""},{"time":597349,"text":"And maybe -- because science is not\nclear on that right now --"},{"time":600666,"text":"it's really just that the brain\nis feeling sympathy with their gut."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605117,"text":"This has yet to grow in evidence\nuntil it can come to practice."},{"time":609599,"text":"But just knowing about\nthese kinds of research"},{"time":612214,"text":"that's out there at the moment"},{"time":614284,"text":"helps me in my daily life."},{"time":616523,"text":"And it makes me think\ndifferently of my moods"},{"time":618867,"text":"and not externalize so much all the time."},{"time":621703,"text":"I feel oftentimes during the day\nwe are a brain and a screen,"},{"time":625996,"text":"and we will tend to look\nfor answers right there"},{"time":628847,"text":"and maybe the work is stupid\nor our neighbor --"},{"time":631146,"text":"but really, moods can also\ncome from within."},{"time":633508,"text":"And just knowing this helped me,"},{"time":635369,"text":"for example, when I sometimes\nwake up too early,"},{"time":638623,"text":"and I start to worry and wander\naround with my thoughts."},{"time":641358,"text":"Then I think, \"Stop.\nWhat did I eat yesterday?"},{"time":644413,"text":"Did I stress myself out too much?"},{"time":646138,"text":"Did I eat too late or something?\""},{"time":648198,"text":"And then maybe get up\nand make myself a tea,"},{"time":650461,"text":"something light to digest."},{"time":652011,"text":"And as simple as that sounds,"},{"time":654110,"text":"I think it's been\nsurprisingly good for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658469,"text":"Step three took me further\naway from our body,"},{"time":663367,"text":"and to really understanding\nbacteria differently."},{"time":666985,"text":"The research we have today\nis creating a new definition"},{"time":670257,"text":"of what real cleanliness is."},{"time":673366,"text":"And it's not the hygiene hypothesis --"},{"time":676923,"text":"I think many maybe know this."},{"time":678328,"text":"So it states that when you have\ntoo little microbes in your environment"},{"time":681894,"text":"because you clean all the time,"},{"time":683519,"text":"that's not really a good thing,"},{"time":685145,"text":"because people get more allergies\nor autoimmune diseases then."},{"time":688843,"text":"So I knew this hypothesis,"},{"time":691085,"text":"and I thought I wouldn't learn so much"},{"time":692962,"text":"from looking at cleanliness in the gut."},{"time":695450,"text":"But I was wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697385,"text":"It turns out,"},{"time":699358,"text":"real cleanliness is not about\nkilling off bacteria right away."},{"time":703347,"text":"Real cleanliness is a bit different."},{"time":705980,"text":"When we look at the facts,"},{"time":707532,"text":"95 percent of all bacteria on this planet\ndon't harm us -- they can't,"},{"time":712396,"text":"they don't have the genes to do so."},{"time":714896,"text":"Many, actually, help us a lot,"},{"time":716961,"text":"and scientists at the moment\nare looking into things like:"},{"time":720222,"text":"Do some bacteria help us clean the gut?"},{"time":722867,"text":"Do they help us digest?"},{"time":724265,"text":"Do they make us put on weight\nor have a lean figure"},{"time":726758,"text":"although we're eating lots?"},{"time":728697,"text":"Are others making us feel more courageous\nor even more resilient to stress?"},{"time":733398,"text":"So you see, there are more questions\nwhen it comes to cleanliness."},{"time":738171,"text":"And, actually, the thing is,\nit's about a healthy balance, I think."},{"time":741469,"text":"You can't avoid the bad all the time."},{"time":743906,"text":"This is simply not possible;"},{"time":745663,"text":"there's always something bad around."},{"time":748094,"text":"So what really the whole deal is\nwhen you look at a clean gut,"},{"time":752793,"text":"it's about having good bacteria,\nenough of them,"},{"time":756639,"text":"and then some bad."},{"time":758444,"text":"Our immune system needs the bad, too,"},{"time":760356,"text":"so it knows what it's looking out for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762918,"text":"So I started having this different\nperspective on cleanliness"},{"time":766377,"text":"and a few weeks later,"},{"time":767787,"text":"I held a talk at my university,"},{"time":769943,"text":"and I made a mistake by 1,000."},{"time":772063,"text":"And I went home and I realized\nin that moment,"},{"time":774521,"text":"I was like, \"Ah! I made\na mistake by 1,000."},{"time":777560,"text":"Oh God, that's so much,\nand that's so embarrassing.\""},{"time":780667,"text":"And I started to think about this,\nI was like, \"Ugh!\""},{"time":783458,"text":"And after a while I said,"},{"time":784673,"text":"\"OK, I made this one mistake,"},{"time":786527,"text":"but then I also told so many\ngood and right and helpful things,"},{"time":790635,"text":"so I think it's OK, you know?"},{"time":792130,"text":"It's a clean thing.\""},{"time":793524,"text":"And then I was like, \"Oh, wait."},{"time":795976,"text":"Maybe I took my perspective\non cleanliness further.\""},{"time":799166,"text":"And it's my theory at the moment\nthat maybe we all do."},{"time":801872,"text":"Take it a bit further than just\ncleaning our living room,"},{"time":804666,"text":"where maybe we make it\nto sort like a life hygiene."},{"time":807796,"text":"Knowing that this is about\nfostering the good"},{"time":811453,"text":"just as much as trying to shelter\nyourself from the bad"},{"time":815116,"text":"had a very calming effect on me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817753,"text":"So in that sense,"},{"time":819233,"text":"I hope today I told you\nmostly good and helpful things,"},{"time":822947,"text":"and thank you for your time,"},{"time":824517,"text":"for listening to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825952,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}